Provenance
----------
This public repository is an extraction of the neutral canon engine surface.
The public source is digest-pinned in consiliency-spec.public-manifest.json.
The vendored Rust crate under canon/core/ declares "MIT" in its own
Cargo.toml package metadata; MIT is Apache-2.0-compatible. The repository as a
whole is offered under Apache-2.0.

